{"tid":646452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有用開止汗劑既巴絲打入","createTime":"2018-04-29T05:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T05:50:24.000Z","uid":179883,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bba8cb9747e9ab615ad673fa35fbc9668359c2fe","tid":646452,"uid":179883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:04:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的 原本同女朋友約左今朝行山<br />\n一開始佢話天氣唔係幾好（但明明勁好太陽）<br />\n之後再講先話做完脫毛冇得搽止汗劑 驚臭親我所以唔去<br />\n我話唔怕啦都一齊咁耐 點會嫌臭 個個做運動都係咁啦<br />\n之後佢話我唔明女仔諗咩 話唔想比唔好既一面比男朋友睇<br />\n最後講多幾句先話 佢唔搽既話冇安全感出遠門同做運動<br />\n係真係會咁？唔搽會有障礙？<br />\n<br />\n正評：yes<br />\n負評：藉口 係懶"},{"pid":"4c160df557c4c4ddb2b901e030c0e84a01df1e43","tid":646452,"uid":171087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"靚女流嘅汗係香<br />\n佢流臭汗咪即係唔靚"},{"pid":"4c6ef9a8b3b2874219422bc2bb5d7d1f72630dbe","tid":646452,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:12:44.000Z","msg":"你地應該未扑過?"},{"pid":"48e57bcc212115d47a8d4f4364c72ab22fe2736e","tid":646452,"uid":68236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:13:50.000Z","msg":"應該係真係覺得天氣唔好<br />\n今日咁曬女仔點會想曬黑"},{"pid":"ad2512165167d3746ab0f51736ecb778b279ea5f","tid":646452,"uid":179883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89645c7b5bbd57508643cb35bf64c932a229187d","tid":646452,"uid":179883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2178e20734a15688175b5ac95eb74bac257e04a3","tid":646452,"uid":49183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T05:31:05.000Z","msg":"可以噴係衫到"},{"pid":"ea37f587dd3c2faeb23173db9a1cce18169e7f50","tid":646452,"uid":179883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2178e20734a15688175b5ac95eb74bac257e04a3","tid":646452,"uid":49183,"lik